The track system was equipped in such a way that electrically operated cars could be used there.
On the Mexican side, access is in a building 80 meters from the border.
According to authorities, a ladder 20 meters into the depth leads to the actual tunnel entrance.
The tunnel has a cross-section of 1.20 meters height and 90 centimeters width.
It would also have been suitable to promote illegal immigration to the United States.
Two of the suspects were arrested in connection with the cocaine discovery.
The third, a Mexican, was caught for the marijuana seized.
All three of them face a maximum sentence of life imprisonment, officials said.
